rows.label: tlk42420151_03_msg0002
rows.name: I feel like the end of Alst is near...

rows.label: tlk42420151_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Chorrul was born in Superbia, so I'm not
fluent in Nopon, and I've never been to any
other country...

rows.label: tlk42420151_03_msg0004
rows.name:
For it to end like this...
it's so sad.

rows.label: tlk42420151_03_msg0005
rows.name:
The Nopon tribe hasn't done anything wrong.
It's all the fault of the Superbians, the Invidians,
and the people of Acedia...
